{"tid":492881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［可有生機］議事規則大戰第一回之泛民怒啪對「手」","createTime":"2017-12-08T03:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T04:17:04.000Z","uid":76713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"24fb594fb7e77c9ce43e488c2a9515a48877eb25","tid":492881,"uid":76713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:16:01.000Z","msg":"立法會昨正式展開《議事規則》修改戰，由於立法會主席梁君彥早已用合併辯論手法封殺拉布，所以民主派一開始就抗爭，多次衝出座位抗議，令大會三度被迫暫停，到傍晚更將行動升級，企圖佔領主席台。梁君彥罕有地未有驅逐議員或宣佈休會，但有保安未經主席指示下，自行將多名泛民議員抬回座位。民主派議員批評，梁君彥為建制派「吹黑哨」，表明即使建制派成功修改《議事規則》，民主派日後亦會全民皆兵，「招呼你哋（建制派）！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171208/57554687\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171208%2F57554687&d=WhVtFhm6MzdxFGSq8%2FK8Qf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=da850e51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171208%2F57554687&h=35846e13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171208/57554687</a><br />\n<br />\n梁君彥正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90977c77b06db86245c300280c3c2ffcef72ba96","tid":492881,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:41:06.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰呢？"},{"pid":"fe6fb1a659c76922e853a2f981f97e6d669f8de8","tid":492881,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T04:17:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鄭松泰呢？</blockquote><br />\n玩緊旗仔"}]}